# App Page Shell

- For new route pages, prefer `AppPageShell` and `AppPageHeader` from `components/layout/AppPageShell`.
- Default page wrapper should be centered: `mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl space-y-6`.
- Use `width="narrow"` only when the page intentionally needs a smaller reading width.
- Do not use bare `max-w-*` page wrappers without `mx-auto`; they left-align inside the app layout.
- Use the current header surface style: `rounded-lg border border-border bg-white p-6 dark:bg-slate-900`.

```tsx
<AppPageShell>
  <AppPageHeader
    title="Module"
    description="Short description"
    icon={<FileText className="h-5 w-5" />}
  />
  <Card className="border-border">...</Card>
</AppPageShell>
```
